  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Having spent many weeks lobbying ministers for a new local government settlement for the constituency, this morning I met with Rishi Sunak MP, Minister for Local Government, to hear details of the new settlement which is to be announced this afternoon. More to follow.<a href="https://t.co/maqfTVuqcH" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/maqfTVuqcH</a></p>

</div>

<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">A merry Christmas to <a href="/HelpStAndrews" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="240306404"><s>@</s><b>HelpStAndrews</b></a> - a wonderful charity long-supported by <a href="/MartinVickers" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="831250927"><s>@</s><b>MartinVickers</b></a>. They provide free care for anyone over the age of 18 with a wide range of progressive life-limiting conditions. Do follow them to see the good work that they do.<a href="https://t.co/aHTjqmTnLc" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/helpstandrews/status/943845036910874624" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/helpstandrews/status/943845036910874624"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/helpstandrews/</span><span class="invisible">status/943845036910874624</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>

          <div class="QuoteTweet-text tweet-text u-dir" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="2" dir="ltr">To help fix our broken housing market, we will increase spending by 2 billion and deliver a new generation of council housing. <span data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>CPC17</b></span> <span class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/QxCkMWf4KT</span></div>

  <ul>

        <div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">We owe it to our children to give serious consideration to the current debate about grammar schools.   <form class="t1-form">

    <div class="embed-destination-wrapper">

    </div>
  </form>
